COMMENT ON COLUMN assistant_turns.user_message IS 'The user''s question text for this turn.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN assistant_turns.assistant_reply IS 'The assistant''s reply text.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN assistant_turns.raw_exchange IS 'Full request/response metadata as raw JSON (messages, system-prompt kind, usage block, finish reason, latency).';
