COMMENT ON COLUMN erb_features.erb_package IS 'FK -> ERBPackages.ERBPackageId. The package this feature belongs to (many features -> one package).';
COMMENT ON COLUMN erb_features.is_licensed IS 'This feature''s own licensing flag. When false, the feature is hidden from non-Effortless users regardless of its package (used to fence off Effortless Elements tooling features). Blank/true = licensed.';
