COMMENT ON COLUMN erb_features.description IS 'What the feature does, in prose.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN erb_features.category IS 'FK to ERBFeatureCategories — the cross-package functional category this feature belongs to (intake / scoring / module / validation / review / output / extraction / prep / dashboard / integration / data-model / platform / devops).';
