  modified_by_model                   TEXT                                      -- Audit: the AI model credited on the last save when an LLM made/assisted the change (e.g. "gpt-4o"). NULL for plain human writes. Read from the app.modified_by_model session GUC by the audit trigger. The owner (CreatedBy/ModifiedBy) is always the human JWT user, never a model.
);
